Requirements of wordle
- should contain everything i need to implement


Wordle
- each guess must be a 5 letter word
- you have 6 tries
- can backspace
- when you press enter
  - Board
    - show past attempt
    - show current attempt
    - correct letter wrong position is blue
    - correct letter correct position is orange
    - wrong letters are gray
    - shake row when word is invalid
  - Keyboard
    - reflects best knowledge of game state
    - if letter is both blue and orange in attempts, letter will be orange
    - attempted letters that are not used are grayed out
    - can input by typing or by pressing keys on Keyboard
  - letter change color with animation one by one
  - current attempt letters have slight light border
